service.name: National Bowel Cancer Screening Register
service.description: The National Bowel Cancer Screening Program aims to detect cancer early and reduce cancer-related deaths. The National Bowel Cancer Screening Register is an important part of the program. The register issues invitation kits, reminder letters and keeps a record of results.
